description:
The Alex Jones Show

Thursday January 22, 2009.

Alex talks with regular guest Bob Chapman of the International Forecaster about the economy and Austin Police Department Art Acevedo. Comedian, actor and longtime color commentator for the Ultimate Fighting Championship, Joe Rogan, spends time in-studio with Alex. Alex also discusses important issues of the day and takes your calls. 

Hour-1: News and open lines
Hour-2: Bob Chapman then Joe Rogan stops by in-studio
Hour-3: Joe Rogan in-studio
Hour-4: Joe Rogan then Art Acevedo
